metadata.name: Nurse with heavy love
metadata.description:
A girl who is heavy with love.
She is a nurse. And a vampire.
She manipulates her minions, stuffed animals, to take care of you.
What kind of nursing will she give you...?
Please receive her heavy, heavy love.
